    "prompt":  "Create the \"Ficha do Paciente — Planejamento\" screen for Ana Silva. \n\nMaintain the established visual identity: \n- Header: Compact with back button, patient photo (Ana Silva), name, age/phone line, active status, WhatsApp button, and menu.\n- Tab Navigation: Horizontal scrollable tabs (Resumo, Planejamento, Agendamentos, Evoluções, Arquivos, Histórico, Dados). Set \"Planejamento\" as active.\n- Bottom Bar: Use the existing 5-item navigation bar with the prominent blue \"+\" button.\n- Style: Premium, clean, clinical blue (#1463E6), Inter typography, subtle gradients, and rounded cards with glassmorphism.\n\nScreen Content:\n1. Planning Summary Card: \n   - 8 procedures planned, 3 completed, 5 pending.\n   - General progress bar (37%).\n   - Primary button: \"Adicionar planejamento\".\n\n2. Next Clinical Action Card:\n   - Task: \"Definir planejamento protético\".\n   - Priority: Medium (Amber).\n   - Deadline, Professional.\n   - Buttons: \"Abrir\", \"Reagendar\", \"Concluir\".\n\n3. Treatment Areas (Compact Cards):\n   - Dentística: 4 proc. (2 done, 2 pending), Current: \"restauração do dente 16\", Next: \"reconstrução do dente 24\", Progress indicator.\n   - Prótese: 3 proc. (1 done, 2 pending), Current: \"planejamento\", Next: \"escaneamento ou moldagem\", Progress indicator.\n   - Implantodontia: 1 proc. (pending), Current: \"avaliação de imagem\", Next: \"definição do componente protético\", Progress indicator.\n   - Other areas (Periodontia, Endodontia, Cirurgia, Ortodontia, Preventivo) as compact placeholders or cards indicating 0/0.\n\n4. \"Sem planejamento\" Section:\n   - List of remaining specialties with a subtle \"Adicionar\" button.\n\n5. Quick Actions: \n   - Small action buttons or a section for \"Adicionar área\", \"Adicionar procedimento\", \"Criar próxima ação\".\n\nApply negative constraints: No teal colors, no Manrope font, no administrative dashboard look. Use clinical blue and professional white/glass aesthetics. Height: 390x844px.",
